        <h3>No endorsement or warranty.</h3>
        <p>Inclusion or visibility does not mean we endorse, vet, or guarantee any Third-Party Service.</p>

        <h3>No custody.</h3>
        <p>We do not take custody of user funds. Interactions with smart contracts or external apps are directly between you and those third parties.</p>

        <h3>Your risk.</h3>
        <p>Smart contracts may be unaudited, exploited, or fail. Tokens may be volatile or worthless. Use your own judgment.</p>

        <h2>4. Quests, Points & Rewards</h2>
