        <p>We may modify, cap, withhold, or discontinue the Rewards Program at any time, with or without notice. We are not obligated to issue or convert points into anything of value.</p>

        <h3>Eligibility & fraud.</h3>
        <p>We may require verification, apply geographic restrictions, and disqualify or claw back rewards for suspected abuse (e.g., sybil accounts, bots, falsified activity).</p>

        <h3>Taxes.</h3>
        <p>You are solely responsible for any taxes related to rewards.</p>

        <h3>Freedom to opt-out.</h3>
        <p>Quests are optional. You decide whether to participate.</p>

        <h2>5. User Content: Ratings & Feedback</h2>
        <p>You may post ratings, tags, and comments ("User Content"). You grant us a worldwide, perpetual, royalty-free license to host, display, adapt, and use User Content to operate and improve the Platform. Don't post anything unlawful, defamatory, misleading, spammy, or infringing (see Acceptable Use).</p>

        <h2>6. Prohibited Conduct (summary)</h2>
        <p>No illegal activity; no circumvention, scraping at scale, or interference; no exploit seeking or reverse-engineering except through an approved security program; no impersonation; no spam/sybil behavior; no attempts to manipulate rankings, quests, or rewards.</p>

        <h2>7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>We own the Platform and all associated content except User Content and third-party marks. Don't use our trademarks without written permission.</p>

        <h2>8. Third-Party Links & Integrations</h2>
        <p>The Platform may link to wallets, bridges, protocols, or other Third-Party Services. We are not responsible for those services and disclaim all liability arising from their use.</p>

