        <h2>10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p><strong>TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, WE SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, EXEMPLARY, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES; LOSS OF PROFITS; LOSS OF DATA; OR SECURITY BREACHES, EVEN IF ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY. IN ALL CASES, OUR AGGREGATE LIABILITY SHALL NOT EXCEED THE GREATER OF (A) USD $100 OR (B) THE AMOUNT YOU PAID US IN THE 12 MONTHS BEFORE THE CLAIM.</strong></p>

        <h2>11. Indemnity</h2>
        <p>You agree to defend, indemnify, and hold harmless [Company] from claims arising out of your use of the Platform, your User Content, or your interactions with Third-Party Services.</p>

        <h2>12. Changes, Suspension, Termination</h2>
        <p>We may update the Platform and these Terms at any time. We may suspend or terminate access (including to the Rewards Program) for any reason, including risk, abuse, or compliance.</p>

        <h2>13. Governing Law; Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by Quebec law, excluding conflict rules. Arbitration/venue: Courts of Quebec. Class-action waiver: disputes must be brought individually.</p>

        <h2>14. Miscellaneous</h2>
        <p>Severability; assignment (we may assign; you may not without consent); force majeure; entire agreement.</p>

        <div class="contact">
          <h3>Contact</h3>
          <p>For questions about these Terms, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:legal@orken.to">legal@orken.to</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
